description:
On today’s show, Emily is talking about why you shouldn’t make assumptions about your partner’s sexual likes and dislikes, and she’s taking your calls.

She covers what to do when you love your sex toys, but your fiancé hasn’t quite come around yet, you keep getting stereotyped as a taker because of how you look – but you’re definitely a giver, and key rules to maintaining something long-distance (hint – it can’t be that way forever).
